thread.title: BRIEF-Gulfport Energy Reports Q1 Net Production Averaged 1,288.6 MMCFE Per Day

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Gulfport Energy Reports Q1 Net Production Averaged 1,288.6 MMCFE Per Day
text:
April 19 (Reuters) - Gulfport Energy Corp:
* GULFPORT ENERGY CORPORATION PROVIDES FIRST QUARTER 2018 PRODUCTION AND PRICING AND SCHEDULES FIRST QUARTER 2018 FINANCIAL AND OPERATIONAL RESULTS CONFERENCE CALL
* GULFPORT ENERGY CORP - QTRLY NET PRODUCTION AVERAGED 1,288.6 MMCFE PER DAY, A 52% INCREASE VERSUS Q1 OF 2017
* GULFPORT ENERGY CORP - QTRLY NET PRODUCTION AVERAGED 1,288.6 MMCFE PER DAY, A 2% INCREASE OVER Q4 OF 2017 AND 52% INCREASE VERSUS Q1 OF 2017
